{"tid":2204212,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"認真想幫中學生手 (大量past paper)","createTime":"2020-09-16T01:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T19:39:40.000Z","uid":296693,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59109b26d1d962a397166a9dbf0991959372e351","tid":2204212,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">認真， 2019年運動， 2020年武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學生簡直<span class=\"red\">無返過學咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出街補習驚有肺炎，係 WhatsApp / TG 班group問問題，又未必有人答到</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">所以我都我用自己小小嘅力量，整咗呢個網站俾大家，目的係比全港咁多位學生一齊幫大家共渡呢個難關。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.brightstars-hk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brightstars-hk.com&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=3c7deba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.brightstars-hk.com</a><br />\n入邊仲有大量 past paper, question bank, notes, 中學 mock etc<br />\n<br />\n比 WhatsApp / telegram / forum 好嘅原因:<br />\n1. 集合全港手足，冇群組人數限制<br />\n2. 每一個答案，全世界都可以見到<br />\n3. 問完問題可以答，答完問題可以問，無分你我，識答嘅就幫<br />\n4. 集合海量文件，網站註冊係英國，唔會俾人 take down <br />\n5. 下載 Wix App 就可以令手機收到通知<br />\n<br />\n🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<span class=\"red\">麻煩各位大學生去幫手答問題<br />\n麻煩各位教師 upload 教學資源<br />\n麻煩各位學生盡情問問題同埋比意見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講真，我自己讀緊書都好忙，所以喺呢個網站度花費嘅時間同精力都有限。但係若果大家真係覺得有用，又可以比意見我點樣改善，我會盡力嘗試幫大家建立一個完美嘅平台。"},{"pid":"29e04a011741de9978a545fc703fcc9a47e20dbc","tid":2204212,"uid":79869,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"59109b26d1d962a397166a9dbf0991959372e351","tid":2204212,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">認真， 2019年運動， 2020年武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學生簡直<span class=\"red\">無返過學咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 